****************************************************************

V-BOX is a sub-system for your biking life which made you more happy.

      verion 1 include:
      	     mcu
	     display
	     gps
	     hall-type speed sensor(s)
	     imu-type posture sensor(s)
	     sd card
	     battery

      version 2 add:
      	     GPRS/3G modem
	     better outside case

      version 3 enable:
      	     modularized design
	     online system
	     mid-range team system
	     EMG module  